    "Id": "chassisdef_fire_wasp_ii_FWSP-II-1",
    "Name": "Fire Wasp II",
    "Details": "The Fire Wasp II is General Motors' heavier Inner Sphere reimagining of the original design, trading raw speed for a considerably more dangerous weapons suite. An ER Large Laser and Artemis IV-guided MML 5 extend its effective range well beyond the original while twin Heavy Flamers and a Retractable Blade make it genuinely threatening up close. Five jump jets keep the chassis mobile and CASE protects all onboard ammunition.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Pilot</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.04</color></b>",
