  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "General Motors saw the Clans rebuild the Fire Wasp and decided the Inner Sphere needed its own answer. Ten tons heavier, proper long-range weapons, Heavy Flamers instead of standard ones, and a Retractable Blade tucked into the right arm. It became one of the most common medium mechs of its era, which tells you something. The Magistracy Highlanders ran these too. Star Corporal Luna Rhodes fought in one right up until Cate's Hold in 3101. That is a name worth remembering.",
